<subSubSection id="A7CC2DBDFFD2FFF9FF6BFE94FE7CFD79" pageId="8" pageNumber="283" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="EF697E36FFD2FFF9FF6BFE94FE0BFD99" blockId="8.[151,1127,370,745]" pageId="8" pageNumber="283">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFD2FFF9FF6BFE94FEB8FE39" bold="true" box="[151,262,370,393]" pageId="8" pageNumber="283">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="8B4703C7FFD2FFF9FEF1FE94FE7BFE39" author="BOROWIEC" box="[269,453,370,393]" firstAuthor="BOROWIEC" journalOrPublisher="Annales Zoologici (Warszawa)" pageId="8" pageNumber="283" pagination="61 - 74" part="55" refId="ref48410" refString="BOROWIEC L. 2005: Six new species of the genus Agroiconota Spaeth, 1913 (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae: Cassidinae), with a key to the genus. Annales Zoologici (Warszawa) 55: 61 - 74." title="Six new species of the genus Agroiconota Spaeth, 1913 (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae: Cassidinae), with a key to the genus" type="journal article" year="2005">BOROWIEC (2005)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFD2FFF9FDC5FE94FCFAFE39" authorityName="Borowiec" authorityYear="2005" box="[569,836,370,393]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Agroiconota" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="283" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="carlobrivioi">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFD2FFF9FDC5FE94FCFAFE39" box="[569,836,370,393]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="283">Agroiconota carlobrivioi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on its unique colour pattern formed by irregular red stripes on yellow elytra while all similar species have regular stripes with complete borders. However, the identity of 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFD2FFF9FCDBFE54FC11FE79" authorityName="Boheman" authorityYear="1855" box="[807,943,434,457]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Coptocycla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="283" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subvittata">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFD2FFF9FCDBFE54FC11FE79" box="[807,943,434,457]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="283">A. subvittata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was erroneously interpreted; its 
<typeStatus id="306DC094FFD2FFF9FEC4FE34FE2BFE59" box="[312,405,466,489]" pageId="8" pageNumber="283">holotype</typeStatus>
has an identical pattern to 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFD2FFF9FD48FE34FCEEFE59" authorityName="Borowiec" authorityYear="2005" box="[692,848,466,489]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Agroiconota" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="283" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="carlobrivioi">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFD2FFF9FD48FE34FCEEFE59" box="[692,848,466,489]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="283">A. carlobrivioi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and is conspecific with it. Therefore I consider 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFD2FFF9FE87FE14FDA6FDB9" authorityName="Borowiec" authorityYear="2005" box="[379,536,498,521]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Agroiconota" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="283" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="carlobrivioi">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFD2FFF9FE87FE14FDA6FDB9" box="[379,536,498,521]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="283">A. carlobrivioi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
a junior subjective synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFD2FFF9FC8BFE14FC41FDB9" authorityName="Boheman" authorityYear="1855" box="[887,1023,498,521]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Coptocycla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="283" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subvittata">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFD2FFF9FC8BFE14FC41FDB9" box="[887,1023,498,521]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="283">A. subvittata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. See also remarks under 
<taxonomicName id="28D605B5FFD2FFF9FECBFDF4FE10FD99" authorityName="Buzzi" authorityYear="1996" box="[311,430,530,553]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Agroiconota" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="283" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="urbanae">
<emphasis id="DDA2A224FFD2FFF9FECBFDF4FE10FD99" box="[311,430,530,553]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="283">A. urbanae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EF697E36FFD2FFF9FF49FDD4FDBDFDD9" blockId="8.[151,1127,370,745]" pageId="8" pageNumber="283">
The 
<typeStatus id="306DC094FFD2FFF9FF18FDD4FEACFDF9" box="[228,274,562,585]" pageId="8" pageNumber="283">type</typeStatus>
locality of 
